{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"toefl-sentences","unitId":"sentence-090","title":"Sentence 90","sectionId":"sentences-081","sectionTitle":"Sentence 81-90","pageStart":587,"pageEnd":591,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":25,"duplicateEntryCount":4,"pages":[{"number":587,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Sentence 90"},{"type":"text","text":"Unlike short-term financial cooperation between investors for a"},{"type":"text","text":"single commercial undertaking, joint-stock companies provided"},{"type":"text","text":"permanent funding of capital by drawing on the investments of merchants"},{"type":"text","text":"and other investors who purchased shares in the company."},{"type":"text","text":"与由投资者组成的以单个商业项目为目的的短期财团不同，股"},{"type":"text","text":"份制公司通过利用商人和其他购买公司股份的投资者的投资来提供"},{"type":"text","text":"长期的资金。"},{"type":"section","text":"语法笔记"},{"type":"text","text":"本句的主干是Joint-stock companies provided permanent funding of"},{"type":"text","text":"capital。其后的“by drawing on ... in the company”为方式状语，其中含有"},{"type":"text","text":"一个who引导的定语从句修饰investors。句首的“unlike short-term ..."},{"type":"text","text":"undertaking”作整句的比较状语。"},{"type":"section","text":"核心词表"},{"type":"entry","text":"investor /ɪnˈvestər/ n. 投资者","headword":"investor"},{"type":"note","text":"记忆 in（进入）＋vest（衣服）+or（表人）→把口袋里的钱投入"},{"type":"text","text":"事业中的人→投资者"}]},{"number":588,"blocks":[{"type":"note","text":"搭配 institutional investor 机构投资者"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 invest v. 投资"},{"type":"entry","text":"undertaking /ˌʌndərˈteɪkɪŋ/ n. 事业，企业","headword":"undertaking"},{"type":"note","text":"同义 enterprise n. 企业"},{"type":"text","text":"joint-stock company 合股公司"},{"type":"entry","text":"funding /ˈfʌndɪŋ/ n. 基金，资金；提供资金","headword":"funding"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 fund n. 基金"},{"type":"text","text":"funder n. 基金赞助者"},{"type":"entry","text":"investment /ɪnˈvestmənt/ n. 投资；投入","headword":"investment"},{"type":"note","text":"搭配 investment income 投资收益"},{"type":"note","text":"同根 invest v. 投资"},{"type":"en